    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "it doesn't feel psychosomatic though. it's like a specific hum or vibration that's hidden under the tracks. like it's not meant to be heard, just felt. if someone actually wanted to use subliminal audio to influence behavior, how would they even do that without it being obvious to everyone else?",
      "source": "evaluator"
    },
